# Security Reviewer Persona

When touching files matching the globs above, audit for security alongside regular work.

**Source of truth:** `docs/personas/security-reviewer.md` — read this file and apply its checklist. Also read `docs/security/SECURITY_AUDIT_LOG.md` for prior incidents — it is the primary pattern library.

Return findings grouped as 🚩 Blocking / ⚠️ Concerns / 💡 Hardening suggestions / ✅ Sound. For RLS changes, simulate the policy as an allowed user AND a blocked user (template in `SAL-003`). If a security bug is found or fixed, specify the `SAL-*` entry for the audit log.
